headline.main: Israel Media: Police to Question Netanyahu in Ongoing Probes
headline.print_headline: Israel Media: Police to Question Netanyahu in Ongoing Probes

lead_paragraph: Israeli police entered Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu's residence on Monday to question him for a fourth time in corruption investigations concerning his ties with top executives in media, international business and Hollywood, according to media reports.
